{"tid":1322573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出面放曬風話唔好打死班狗","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:18:56.000Z","uid":24227,"like":160,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"87b34662de39ab7d698a0441327ee095871f92b2","tid":1322573,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFKqpFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFKqpFB.png&h=098fbf3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖所示<br />\n話打死警會民意逆轉<br />\n<br />\n首先，班狗基本上曬gear<br />\n武器精良，對比我地班示威者<br />\n俾你打都係用雨遮擋，弱雞到不得了<br />\n撞立法會玻璃都係用紙皮車咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其次，我地班手足俾佢地棍棍狠勁扑頭扑面<br />\n食催淚煙胡椒搞到哮喘發作甚至心臟停頓<br />\n開槍近距離𣈴頭𣈴肚射<br />\n我地都未死得啦！<br />\n你同班狗擔心佢地俾示威者打死？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有條友開post 話班狗俾雨遮插面會死<br />\n簡直匪疑所思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該大家冷靜少少好唔好<br />\n<br />\n其實到咗依一刻，民意已經好清晰 <br />\n你諗吓班教會左膠和理非都大和解曬<br />\n講明不分割去支持<br />\n市民都由以前只接受遊行示威<br />\n到依家師奶阿叔開始接受同理解年輕人勇武抗爭<br />\n相反撐警嘅人由始至終都唔會改變立場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家要驚民意逆轉嘅係政府<br />\n係班狗<br />\n唔係我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d673e1586531e10f9cfb707f5a357793789c3f0","tid":1322573,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"好呀"},{"pid":"8c7ad34fd453b618ad4de1d12e6114ff4382354c","tid":1322573,"uid":8600,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"71夠話棄守立會民意逆轉啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d557fc75e9237ecb33f7be09269c9aea4c6dada0","tid":1322573,"uid":215876